  "records": {
    "description": "The slice logic is almost the same as a hopper speed merger, but uses hopper minecarts to achieve four-speed merging",
    "features": [
      "4x hopper speed merging.",
      "Hopper minecarts auto-recover when idle, with no entities.",
      "Fully Hopper Locked.",
      "It has a built-in fill level comparer, and after merging, the output goes through a fill level sorter.",
      "Expandable."
    ],
    "notes": "* A pair of partial boxes must be input simultaneously and at a period no less than 25gt.\n* Each unit expansion requires adding 6gt to the box distribution period."
